---
title: Shawarma-Spiced Chicken & Feta Wraps with Feta, Cucumber & Scallion Yogurt Sauce
description: Whip up your favorite spiced chicken wrap any time with our spin on the beloved street cart classic. Load up flour tortillas with nutty bulgur pilaf with feta and tomato, warmly spiced chicken, refreshing cucumber, and a tangy yogurt sauce to balance all the flavors. Whether it’s for now or to-go, this is a wrap you’ll keep coming back for.
